==============================
📘 OSI MODEL - MEMORY TRICK
==============================

🔹 Memory Trick:
All People Seem To Need Data Processing


🔹 Breakdown:

All        → Application Layer (7)
People     → Presentation Layer (6)
Seem       → Session Layer (5)
To         → Transport Layer (4)
Need       → Network Layer (3)
Data       → Data Link Layer (2)
Processing → Physical Layer (1)


🔹 OSI Layers (Top → Bottom)

7. Application   → User interaction (Browser, Apps)
6. Presentation  → Encryption, Formatting (HTTPS)
5. Session       → Connection start/end (Login)
4. Transport     → Data delivery (TCP/UDP)
3. Network       → Routing (IP Address)
2. Data Link     → Local delivery (MAC Address)
1. Physical      → Hardware (Cable, WiFi)



